author: sethlee
title: mini racer
review: this set may not fit lego people but it could be a nice safari car it could might be a very nice key chain for backpacks and more it is a very nice racer I wish they still sell it in stores lego creater is the best.

author: Yoda____
title: Kabaya sweets?
review: I got this set free with a meal at legoland but still. This is a nice set and it looks rather charming. For me, when it comes free sets, as long as they are charming they deserve a 5. After all they are free and beggars can't be choosers.

author: Alemas
title: Kabaya?
review:
I got this from LEGOLAND Windsor! I have three of these! Anyway, it has a simple design, with a trans-neon green 2x4 slope brick. It's, as the other reviewer said, charming!

Pros:

Simple design
Useful pieces
Charming

Cons:

None!

Overall, if you have three or four of these, make a race!
